For Screaming Vlog 36 we meet up with @salba69, @twistthewrist, @jake_wooten, and @catchsurf Pros @kalanirobb, @johnnyredmond, and @tylerstanaland at Catch Surf HQ in Encinitas, CA! Catch Surf’s @beefs_official gives us a bit of insight on the brand, and explains the similarities between SC and Catch Surf.
